2169640.png", "id": "1024146142213818", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982441_1024146145547151_3805722331130364725_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=nYdk880ISHsQ7kNvgGPiIhE&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AxvZpfOunlcSMlFS6sxrkYm&oh=00_AYDCY4hjVivCR0hwpZ0iwLFtjlnRnaZINRNulQZcgQoGxg&oe=66EEB3D7"}, {"file_name": "OculusScreenshot1702168716.png", "id": "1045546456768821", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031557_1045546460102154_8869584294705848419_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=nPnas9F-4XcQ7kNvgFYZz9q&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AxvZpfOunlcSMlFS6sxrkYm&oh=00_AYDl5RGTfY-GLdgn4q3rDsmDgHUtSXg004SuBmCeWyEVGQ&oe=66EEA194"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "OculusScreenshot1702169579.png", "id": "1421996451722456", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974657_1421996455055789_5575213174514540843_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ukbWPIleDE0Q7kNvgEOXQqa&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AxvZpfOunlcSMlFS6sxrkYm&oh=00_AYDgdhDeaDV7O9PsBgj08Yc9ce0h2UK_zXXmG5neh9cOhA&oe=66EE98DC"}, "display_name": "StarGateVR", "keywords": [], "long_description": "StarGateVR represents a breakthrough in astronomical research and collaboration, offering a virtual reality application uniquely designed for the exploration of stars based on Gaia or other star database queries. This innovative tool allows users and their collaborators to immerse themselves in a shared virtual space, where the downloaded star parameters, selected 3 at a time, are rendered in three-dimensional detail. By leveraging the power of VR technology, StarGateVR provides an unparalleled platform for interactive learning, analysis, and discovery in the field of astronomy.", "short_description": "Use VR to view, explore, analyze, and collaborate on multi-parameter Gaia Archive star data."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.immsci.com/